      "role": "user",
      "content": "something really weird happened on my drive to work today. i was passing that same gray utility building on the corner of 5th and main and i swear the window pattern just... repeated. like, it was the exact same smudge and crack in the glass, identical, right next to the first one. it felt like a glitch in a video game or something. have u ever heard of people seeing stuff like that?",
